export getSimilarFunctions(dir:string,options:Object=)→resolve,findJSFiles,extractSignatures,allSignatures.push,calculateSimilarity,pairs.push|extract and compare signatures across directory for similar pairs
PATTERNS: structural hashing of control flow|pair-wise comparison scoring
EDGE_CASES: skips very small functions|ignores overloads (same name/file)